metadata.name: Sweet-eyed Melis
metadata.description:
This pretty girl is the only daughter who did our job as a guard in our fields when I visited my village. it's so cute that he stole my heart by saying, "can i pose for you?" After our sweet little talk, he gave us this beautiful pose. Melis, it was so beautiful that I spent the day kissing her before I could shoot too many frames. He said he lived in the village with the family and loved the village. He gave me that pose himself. I put it on my wall by pressing this frame of natural pose and natural light. This shot won a prize in the contest held in the city where I lived. This yellow and warm square warms me up.

Artis: Metin Burak KINACILAR
